        <li>How any fees/fares will be calculated.</li>
        <li>What day(s) each PSV vehicle will be used and for how many hours each day – you must give the maximum figures this could be in any given week.</li>
        <li>A detailed breakdown of the days and hours you plan to carry out the work needed to run your PSV operation safely, effectively and profitably.</li>
        <li>A copy of your business plan for the PSV operation – this should outline the following:
          <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--number">
