          </ul>
        </li>
        <li>The full names of the people who will be driving the PSVs if known and a copy of both sides of their driving licence as evidence of their relevant driving category entitlement.</li>
      </ul>
      <h3 class="govuk-heading-s">Drivers hours and working time</h3>
      <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet govuk-list--spaced">
        <li>If the partnership’s main occupation involves driving you must provide details of how many hours you would spend driving in a typical week and a heavy week.</li>
        <li>How will you make sure that you/your drivers will be compliant with drivers hours/working time rules if your licence were granted.</li>
        <li>If any of the partners intend to be a driver, will the hours they spend on your main occupation be reduced to accommodate the hours spent driving/operating your PSV – if so, you must tell us:
          <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--number govuk-list--spaced">
            <li>What the new hours and days per week will be.</li>
            <li>What the new weekly/monthly/yearly income will be.</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

